connect20/flickrocket.name: connect20/Flickrocket

suggest.magento-hackathon/magento-composer-insta: Allows to manage this package as a dependency

connect20/flickrocket.description: This extension enables you to sell and rent (optionally DRM protected) digital content such as DVDs (incl. all menus, bonus material, etc.), video (HD+SD), audio books, ebooks  (epub and PDF) and packaged content such as HTML, Flash, images, etc.
